{"tid":1768613,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日，仲吹奏屎為嘅，祝你地入晒監獄","createTime":"2019-12-04T07:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:31:03.000Z","uid":12628,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee2969a04b7ff2da232bb4a69cc307e28cd40a7","tid":1768613,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767565\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767565</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買屎為，就不如自己直接送中算喇！<br />\n唔好同我講電話唔係政治，屎為產品本身就係政治，而且係制度同霸權暴力！間諜機構！<br />\n屎為本身軟件垃圾，硬件除影相外，根本唔入流！平時降人頻扮慳電，一唔降頻打機就發燒兼倒水，欺瞞消費者！<br />\n係連登請埋啲扮中立嘅打手，扮消費者借啲依推部google  service 都無嘅岸鳩機！<br />\n你老母湊大你咁辛苦去做屎為契弟，幫支共侵犯明文明世界，你班5毛人渣，祝你地世世為奴啦，撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae2c54cb03247931bdd86bada1d91e7104da635","tid":1768613,"uid":77532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐監嘅<br />\n拘留251日啦"},{"pid":"94aa3c99dec2aa64b8d72b95c46dd0a0fbe4e779","tid":1768613,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"我地場抗爭，啲手足犧牲咁大，拉嘅拉，打嘅打，傷嘅傷，死嘅死！<br />\n咁大犧牲，如果仲有人用屎為，幫支共助紂為虐！<br />\n你老味，一定係5毛，廢老，人渣！<br />\n我地唔單止要杯葛，而且要圍而屌之"},{"pid":"b1482510cc1f18a77158fa1d84f1dbdb9ea651a9","tid":1768613,"uid":12628,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"5ae2c54cb03247931bdd86bada1d91e7104da635","tid":1768613,"uid":77532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗坐監嘅<br />\n拘留251日啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"251暗藏玄機<br />\n2+5+1=8<br />\n2*5-1=9<br />\n2+5-1=6<br />\n5-2+1=4<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/